        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">center</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Table 1</ENAMEX>) [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">15</TIMEX> ] . We used a second scale to
