            <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">group</ENAMEX> also received a video system that allowed
            real-time remote interaction with the health system [
            <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">24</NUMEX> ] . Both <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">groups</ENAMEX> had comparable compliance with
            medication regimen, knowledge about their <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">disease</ENAMEX>,
