            <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">12</NUMEX>-item Short-Form <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Health Survey</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">SF</ENAMEX>-<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">12</NUMEX>)™.
            The other studies described the use of videophones
            for <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patient</ENAMEX> communication with health care providers.
            In a study in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Japan</ENAMEX>, <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">16</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">elderly patients</ENAMEX> who were
